						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Madanagōpāla temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadāśiva, 1547 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1469, Plavaṅga, Mārgaśira śu. 12</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1547 A.D., November 24, (Thursday).</hi></p>						

						<p>It seems to record the remission of taxes on barbers by Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara Rāmarājayyadēva-mahārāju. Mentions Koṇḍōju, the barber.</p>						

						</summary>
