<p>
<lb n="1"/>svastiśrī jayābhyudaya śāli 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vāhana śakhavaru<unclear>ṣaṁbulu</unclear> 
<lb n="3"/>1469 Agunēṭi plavaṁga saṁ 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vvatsara mārgaśira śu 1<unclear>2</unclear>lu śrī 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ma<unclear>drā</unclear>jādhirāja paramēśvara 
<lb n="6"/>śrīvīrapratāpa śrī sadāsivadē 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>va mahārāyaluṁgāru vija 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>yanagaramaṁddu sā<unclear>mrā</unclear>jyani 
<lb n="9"/>yēlucuṁḍaṁgānu śrīma 
<lb n="10" break="no"/><unclear>ṁ</unclear>mahāmaṁḍalēśvara rāma 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>rājayya dēvamahārāju 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>luṁgāru vijayanagaraṁ ma 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṁgaḷa koṁḍōjukunū rāya 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>siṁhāsanānaku cellē <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="15"/><unclear>paṁ</unclear>nu maṁgaḷa vōjulakunu I <note n="170-1">The is fixed into the wall.</note> 
</p>

